{"operationName":"User","variables":{},"query":"query User {
  user {
    id
    email
    active
    emailConfirmed
    recoveryEnabled
    kycLevel
    accountType
    kycStatuses {
      level
      status
      levelName
      __typename
    }
    personal {
      userId
      firstName
      lastName
      countryOfResidence
      dateOfBirth
      termsOfServiceAgreement
      privacyPolicyAgreement
      subscriptionAgreement
      thirdPartyAgreement
      phone
      phoneCountry
      sfUserId
      city
      postalCode
      state
      street
      building
      apartment
      countryOfIssuance
      identificationNumber
      __typename
    }
    assets {
      title
      assetId
      providerId
      displaySymbol
      baseUnit
      icon
      type
      balance
      __typename
    }
    container {
      smsMigrationRequired
      isNeedOnlyProviderActions
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}

{"operationName":"InvestBank","variables":{"pageSize":100},"query":"query InvestBank($search: String, $pageSize: Int) {
  investBank {
    id
    name
    logoImage
    kycRequired
    config
    projectsWithCategories(search: $search, pageSize: $pageSize) {
      projects {
        id
        title
        description
        shortDescription
        link
        country
        logoImage
        coverImage
        offeringType
        instrumentType
        startDate
        endDate
        softCap
        hardCap
        tokensTotal
        tokensSold
        initialOfferingPrice
        priceInUSD
        liquidationPrice
        category
        categoryId
        projectAsset {
          icon
          providerId
          __typename
        }
        minInvestmentInUSD
        offeringSize
        projectPair {
          id
          assetIdToken0
          assetIdToken1
          balance0
          balance1
          traderFee
          isActive
          address
          dirty
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      categories {
        id
        name
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}

  user {
    id
    email
    active
    emailConfirmed
    recoveryEnabled
    kycLevel
    accountType
    kycStatuses {
      level
      status
      levelName
      __typename
    }
    personal {
      userId
      firstName
      lastName
      countryOfResidence
      dateOfBirth
      termsOfServiceAgreement
      privacyPolicyAgreement
      subscriptionAgreement
      thirdPartyAgreement
      phone
      phoneCountry
      sfUserId
      city
      postalCode
      state
      street
      building
      apartment
      countryOfIssuance
      identificationNumber
      __typename
    }
    assets {
      title
      assetId
      providerId
      displaySymbol
      baseUnit
      icon
      type
      balance
      __typename
    }
    container {
      smsMigrationRequired
      isNeedOnlyProviderActions
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}

requests.postData:
{"operationName":"InvestBank","variables":{"pageSize":100},"query":"query InvestBank($search: String, $pageSize: Int) {
  investBank {
    id
    name
    logoImage
    kycRequired
    config
    projectsWithCategories(search: $search, pageSize: $pageSize) {
      projects {
        id
        title
        description
        shortDescription
        link
        country
        logoImage
        coverImage
        offeringType
        instrumentType
        startDate
        endDate
        softCap
        hardCap
        tokensTotal
        tokensSold
        initialOfferingPrice
        priceInUSD
        liquidationPrice
        category
        categoryId
        projectAsset {
          icon
          providerId
          __typename
        }
        minInvestmentInUSD
        offeringSize
        projectPair {
          id
          assetIdToken0
          assetIdToken1
          balance0
          balance1
          traderFee
          isActive
          address
          dirty
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      categories {
        id
        name
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}
